Subject: ASK: bridge fast-path hooks (CPE_FAST_PATH)

Adds the brevent notifier chain (port-down + FDB-update events)
consumed by the CDX OOT module, the CONFIG_CPE_FAST_PATH skb fields
(abm_ff, expt_pkt, iif_index, underlying_iif, underlying_vlan_tci,
qosmark) plus copy-paths in __copy_skb_header / __skb_clone /
skb_scrub_packet, and a few hookable taps in br_input/br_fdb/
br_forward/br_vlan/br_stp_if for the fast-path.

Refreshed for Linux 6.18.x: regenerated from a fuzz-clean apply
against linux-6.18.26 (no semantic change). Offsets shifted in
skbuff.c (+112..+324), br_fdb.c (+11..+147), br_private.h (+9..+11).

